      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The engine runs consistently and the transmission shifts through all gears, but you may notice some minor fluid seeps and a suspension that feels a bit soft. Cosmetically, there are several noticeable scratches and small dings on the exterior, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear and some staining. While it is fully functional and road-ready, a new owner should expect to address some upcoming maintenance items and minor cosmetic touch-ups to bring it back to its best.",
