      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project! This vehicle is the perfect choice for a dedicated hobbyist or mechanic looking for a diamond in the rough. While it currently requires significant mechanical repairs and bodywork to get back to its best, it offers a fantastic foundation and a great entry point into car restoration at a budget-friendly price!",
